subject: Refactor SoftwareInventory to request the interfaces it uses
commitMessage:
Refactor SoftwareInventory to request the interfaces it uses

`xyz.openbmc_project.Software.Activation` is used for SoftwareInventory,
but it is not requested in the dbus call. Refactor the SoftwareVersion
dbus call and added the request for `Activation` to make sure that we
have the right information.

This will allow different services to provide the information for
`xyz.openbmc_project.Software.Activation` when the dbus back filename()
matches. If `Activation` and `Version` is always from the same service,
there will be no visible change.

TESTED: WIP

Change-Id: Ib497b23b206315ab22caedc22a12d1a5984d7c13
Signed-off-by: Willy Tu <wltu@google.com>
